{"tid":47213,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"條90後竟然話聽日冬至要早走 !","createTime":"2016-12-20T07:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T09:59:56.000Z","uid":62722,"like":5,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1490995c4cbb77655723d7fb4602155f780184fd","tid":47213,"uid":62722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:50:34.000Z","msg":"話說聽日係中國d唔知咩節日冬至<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁呢，有條友話咩冬至，聽日要早走話同家人做節 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就緊係唔批啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後仲畀我偷偷聽到佢講粗口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我而家諗住聽日畀多d野佢做，搞到佢ot <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時就話有幾憎中國乜乜物物，而家就話要做節，根本就想借d意蛇王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩我醒目識穿佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189474f107f25fab2ff4283cea8f622762292409","tid":47213,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:52:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f635d3edd9dbdf0524174af8cd51702a538a5415","tid":47213,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:52:23.000Z","msg":"Ching Ho ball<br />\n90後寫蛇王就搵埋啲唔知咩嘅藉口<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比佢o下t就啱"},{"pid":"4cdd148af0f8edd5090cb8e8bd19a7cb312bbadf","tid":47213,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ching Ho ball<br />\n90後想蛇王就搵埋啲唔知咩嘅藉口<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比佢o下t就啱</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a32cc0393ffb5e4f09a8241aa2d57bc6c7222e61","tid":47213,"uid":66283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:53:20.000Z","msg":"你農曆新年唔好放假囉"},{"pid":"e02b27777